<h2>a5 - Synaesthesia</h2>
<p>With this video I tried to illustrate a love story between two creatures. As the lights move, the creatures communicate and throughout the video their sounds will be less dissonant ultil they match the background guitar. I used panning automation to create the sense that each creature was speaking from one side.  
